creator: VOODOO
descriptionHtml: The most fun word game! You've got to work out a five letter word. Start off with any word and then you will told which letters are not in the word at all, in the wrong place or in the right place. So you need to then see how quickly you can get the right five letter word. It's so much simpler than it sounds and you'll be playing again and again. Enjoy!
